title: League of Legends Complete Sound Effects Pack [FLAC]
description:
League of Legends Complete Sound Effects Pack [FLAC]

Contains SFX upto the release of Yasuo (Dec. 2013)

Voice SFX (taunts, jokes, laughs, etc.) are contained within the "VOBank_en_US" folder.

The folders for each champion ("LoL_SFX_[name]) contain mostly grunts and SFX pertaining to the character's skills and attacks.

Background music is contained within the folders: "GameMusicEvents_bank00" and "LoL_MUS_map12".


Files: 20001
Folders: 268
Total Size (Extracted): 3.63GB
